{"tid":585359,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲加：眾槍手忘記自己原本實力","createTime":"2018-03-08T14:42:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-08T15:55:31.000Z","uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d69f1da33188684cef61fbc54b68104b4b313520","tid":585359,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T14:42:43.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴各項賽事慘遭4連敗，球隊狀態低迷。領隊雲加一方面認為球員求勝心切而影響表現，另一問題則在於球員因連敗失去自信，忘記了本身應有實力。<br />\n<br />\n3分鐘入2球 祖記反勝熱刺闖8強<br />\n<br />\n「兵工廠」明晨將於歐霸盃16強賽事首回合作客AC米蘭，由於球隊近日已經4連敗，故這場賽事對眾將以至領隊雲加來說是非勝不可。賽前雲加則強調球員在低谷也應要保持平常心，否則將更難踢出水準：「首先，我想球員們太想贏了，結果反而受影響。我們都太易忘記了本身的實力，而我希望他們可以專注找出自己的問題，然後再想法子改善自己場上做得未夠好的地方，<span style=\"color: red;\">對於近日的成績反而不應過份擔心</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n雲加明日將會面對加度素領軍的AC米蘭，對於這名上任不久的少帥，他笑言自己應重對方身上學習，「他近況很好，而我們卻不太如意，故我才需要從他身上偷師。」"},{"pid":"c1024ce4b6418c5950071f1b81a7ed82da6aa4e7","tid":585359,"uid":109491,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T14:46:05.000Z","msg":"係忘記點撚樣踢波"},{"pid":"4b10c4e7e8547f0bcd60aede22c1919d4d67fbaf","tid":585359,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T15:02:27.000Z","msg":"求勝心切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n完全睇唔到有心機踢波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dc49ea637b2adf44f23a632f3d55b3483014491","tid":585359,"uid":18646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1024ce4b6418c5950071f1b81a7ed82da6aa4e7","tid":585359,"uid":109491,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T14:46:05.000Z","msg":"係忘記點撚樣踢波"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T15:42:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"918f8cca14a597a456399e63153a68ba7749ac73","tid":585359,"uid":114483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T15:50:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係忘記點撚樣踢波</blockquote><br />\n真，得罪講句，球員既罪仲大撚過雲加"},{"pid":"c4e0f5d6f648658d80c53c322959b31c70537f13","tid":585359,"uid":34962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T15:52:27.000Z","msg":"成績已經反映咗成隊波真正實力啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b46a430fc29062f6b89b95de594b6f93dfd9ad70","tid":585359,"uid":13718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T15:55:31.000Z","msg":"雲爺爺收手番大學做professor 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}